 NON-DISCLOSURE AGREEMENT\n\nThis agreement (\u201cAgreement\u201d) is entered into as of the date first written below (the \u201cEffective Date\u201d) by and between TRANSNET LIMITED (hereinafter referred to as \u201cTransnet\u201d or \u201cthe Disclosing Party\u201d) having as its principal place of business at 38 th Floor,", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 451, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "0457ce65-e9c3-4ba4-959d-7a968fb51687": {"__data__": {"id_": "0457ce65-e9c3-4ba4-959d-7a968fb51687", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "719f133b-889a-47be-9bf0-7d3f7f8410c1", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "92b7d2ea440ec941bb40fc2a3da8a123eb3043a7567dc8b5cdbde4ec92b6bb44", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "c65cbe95-e96a-4b7d-8618-2442c2f394cd", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "068b963333e3a8c14945d3517b8c18fb9cae637291faf5757e3620a1290601c0", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "a334954a-227f-4cb3-abf2-86ce903a6be0", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "481592aeef3731ab5c7d399e5d6da21d14438270adeadf4cfbb9d282ed0fb7ad", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Carlton Centre, Johannesburg, 2001, and ___________________________________ (Registration number____________________)  (hereinafter referred to as \u201cthe Bidder\u201d or the \u201cReceiving Party\u201d) with its principal place of business at __________________________________________ (Transnet and the Bidder shall hereinafter referred to as the \u201cParties\u201d).", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 452, "end_char_idx": 794, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "a334954a-227f-4cb3-abf2-86ce903a6be0": {"__data__": {"id_": "a334954a-227f-4cb3-abf2-86ce903a6be0", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "719f133b-889a-47be-9bf0-7d3f7f8410c1", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "92b7d2ea440ec941bb40fc2a3da8a123eb3043a7567dc8b5cdbde4ec92b6bb44", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "0457ce65-e9c3-4ba4-959d-7a968fb51687", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "ab21ef9a9dc91a76d4572ba8f66dba373c99c45333700f90e3b05936c8062b11", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "6bf2c0e0-012b-4162-832c-65f174b2906e", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "8ee7c3c0b36e8f71333ccfe9d396bb9a97505335024e64f8440b9dfa0bdb638e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "WHEREAS, the Bidder is interested in participating in the disposal process being undertaken by Transnet in relation to the business of Luxrail (hereinafter referred to as \u201cthe Blue Train\u201d or \u201cthe Target\u201d) (such disposal hereinafter referred to as the \u201cProposed Transaction\u201d);\nAND WHEREAS, it is agreed that in order to enable the Bidder to assess the Target, Transnet will disclose Confidential Information relevant to the Proposed Transaction to the Bidder;", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 796, "end_char_idx": 1254, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "6bf2c0e0-012b-4162-832c-65f174b2906e": {"__data__": {"id_": "6bf2c0e0-012b-4162-832c-65f174b2906e", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "719f133b-889a-47be-9bf0-7d3f7f8410c1", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "92b7d2ea440ec941bb40fc2a3da8a123eb3043a7567dc8b5cdbde4ec92b6bb44", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "a334954a-227f-4cb3-abf2-86ce903a6be0", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "481592aeef3731ab5c7d399e5d6da21d14438270adeadf4cfbb9d282ed0fb7ad", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "653e0722-6fc6-47aa-802d-0ef181f44fcb", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "12db4abad4803de9cb54b2ccaec25be7c668f76a0650f83aa6f9d040f72c0240", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "AND WHEREAS, the Bidder recognises that careful protection and non-disclosure by the Bidder of Confidential Information disclosed by Transnet is of vital importance to the prosperity of the Target, Transnet and clientele of Transnet;\nNOW THEREFORE, Transnet agrees to disclose the Confidential Information and the Bidder agrees to receive the Confidential Information under the following terms and conditions.\n\n1. CONFIDENTIAL INFORMATION\n\n1.1 Definition.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1257, "end_char_idx": 1712, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "653e0722-6fc6-47aa-802d-0ef181f44fcb": {"__data__": {"id_": "653e0722-6fc6-47aa-802d-0ef181f44fcb", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "719f133b-889a-47be-9bf0-7d3f7f8410c1", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "92b7d2ea440ec941bb40fc2a3da8a123eb3043a7567dc8b5cdbde4ec92b6bb44", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "6bf2c0e0-012b-4162-832c-65f174b2906e", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "8ee7c3c0b36e8f71333ccfe9d396bb9a97505335024e64f8440b9dfa0bdb638e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "2695e432-615c-409d-ba63-7f45e69883cd", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "ef2fd12432e97908197de1b6b163236bb7a07f7b261c94d98e690f6a67c4cfa2", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "When used herein,\n\n Confidential Information shall mean any information and data (in electronic form, in hard copy or given verbally) of a confidential or proprietary nature which is disclosed by the Disclosing Party to the Receiving Party, including but not limited to, group corporate strategy and initiatives, customer information, Target information, proprietary technical, financial, personnel and/or commercial information with respect to the Proposed Transaction, Transnet or the Target and any information which is disclosed pursuant to this", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1713, "end_char_idx": 2262, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "2695e432-615c-409d-ba63-7f45e69883cd": {"__data__": {"id_": "2695e432-615c-409d-ba63-7f45e69883cd", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "719f133b-889a-47be-9bf0-7d3f7f8410c1", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "92b7d2ea440ec941bb40fc2a3da8a123eb3043a7567dc8b5cdbde4ec92b6bb44", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "653e0722-6fc6-47aa-802d-0ef181f44fcb", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "12db4abad4803de9cb54b2ccaec25be7c668f76a0650f83aa6f9d040f72c0240", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "ec0a89a9-bb4f-4b01-ae64-265e9119beab", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "b4779490b248b263cbc0c13980523a064026406616f1c01280f35ddf4480b8df", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Agreement and marked \u201cConfidential\u201d by the Disclosing Party. Confidential information specifically excludes the following:\n\n1.1.\n\n1.1  information which is in the public domain or enters the public domain other than by reason of a breach of the terms of this Agreement;\n\n1.1.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2265, "end_char_idx": 2540, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "ec0a89a9-bb4f-4b01-ae64-265e9119beab": {"__data__": {"id_": "ec0a89a9-bb4f-4b01-ae64-265e9119beab", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "719f133b-889a-47be-9bf0-7d3f7f8410c1", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "92b7d2ea440ec941bb40fc2a3da8a123eb3043a7567dc8b5cdbde4ec92b6bb44", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "2695e432-615c-409d-ba63-7f45e69883cd", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "ef2fd12432e97908197de1b6b163236bb7a07f7b261c94d98e690f6a67c4cfa2", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "986a4ecb-9ffc-4d4d-81dd-e0604d6adc62", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "4a73f740f378b7173c2107b962d9b341eace3df35dcb79807410d2f8566bcce1", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "1.2 where it becomes available to the Receiving Party on a non-confidential basis from a source other than the Disclosing Party or the individual members of the Disclosing Party, as the case may be;\n\n1.1.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2542, "end_char_idx": 2746, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "986a4ecb-9ffc-4d4d-81dd-e0604d6adc62": {"__data__": {"id_": "986a4ecb-9ffc-4d4d-81dd-e0604d6adc62", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "719f133b-889a-47be-9bf0-7d3f7f8410c1", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "92b7d2ea440ec941bb40fc2a3da8a123eb3043a7567dc8b5cdbde4ec92b6bb44", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "ec0a89a9-bb4f-4b01-ae64-265e9119beab", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "b4779490b248b263cbc0c13980523a064026406616f1c01280f35ddf4480b8df", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "1fb5d532-e766-4e4c-8dec-6424264a6a57", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "4784ed54ae80ba2512c03b6068596fe5f043e2d32d14e7486a7f8701f6935bdc", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "1.3 where it was known to the Receiving Party prior to having access to the Confidential information; and\n\n1.1.4  where the Receiving Party is obliged to disclose by law,\n\n or by order or under the rules of any competent regulatory authority or court.\n\n1.2 Purpose.\n\n The purpose of the disclosure of Confidential Information is to enable the Target\u2019s assets and liabilities relevant to the Proposed Transaction to be assessed.\n\n1.3 Ownership.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2748, "end_char_idx": 3191, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "1fb5d532-e766-4e4c-8dec-6424264a6a57": {"__data__": {"id_": "1fb5d532-e766-4e4c-8dec-6424264a6a57", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "719f133b-889a-47be-9bf0-7d3f7f8410c1", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "92b7d2ea440ec941bb40fc2a3da8a123eb3043a7567dc8b5cdbde4ec92b6bb44", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "986a4ecb-9ffc-4d4d-81dd-e0604d6adc62", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "4a73f740f378b7173c2107b962d9b341eace3df35dcb79807410d2f8566bcce1", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "0a71b2f1-be1a-4e03-a628-0956d095a61e", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "4712e1fa3b4d9cd45927a63b5110c68fd266ce46610bcccb17b25ac25961ed28", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "The Confidential Information is and shall be considered valuable trade secrets owned exclusively by the Disclosing Party. The Disclosing Party retains all right, title and interest in the Confidential Information and any reasonably related information which may be subsequently developed, and the Receiving Party waives all rights to the intellectual property and copyright therein in favour of the Disclosing Party.\n\n1.4 No License.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3194, "end_char_idx": 3627, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "0a71b2f1-be1a-4e03-a628-0956d095a61e": {"__data__": {"id_": "0a71b2f1-be1a-4e03-a628-0956d095a61e", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "719f133b-889a-47be-9bf0-7d3f7f8410c1", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "92b7d2ea440ec941bb40fc2a3da8a123eb3043a7567dc8b5cdbde4ec92b6bb44", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "1fb5d532-e766-4e4c-8dec-6424264a6a57", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "4784ed54ae80ba2512c03b6068596fe5f043e2d32d14e7486a7f8701f6935bdc", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "45d33ea7-0ed7-43a6-82e6-790328a76d73", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "4a44084fb8c3bccc553ac1c4ecf5110b84bd78587fdaef2b2f0f2e89a7354e12", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "No license is granted to the Receiving Party in relation to any intellectual property rights that attach to or may be embodied in any Confidential Information, or is implied by the conveying of such Confidential Information to the Receiving Party.\n\n1.5 No Warranties.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3630, "end_char_idx": 3897, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "45d33ea7-0ed7-43a6-82e6-790328a76d73": {"__data__": {"id_": "45d33ea7-0ed7-43a6-82e6-790328a76d73", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "719f133b-889a-47be-9bf0-7d3f7f8410c1", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "92b7d2ea440ec941bb40fc2a3da8a123eb3043a7567dc8b5cdbde4ec92b6bb44", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "0a71b2f1-be1a-4e03-a628-0956d095a61e", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "4712e1fa3b4d9cd45927a63b5110c68fd266ce46610bcccb17b25ac25961ed28", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "d441c1fb-b051-4318-8f77-ee2d5d5584d8", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "d96afd03fa68d282ddbf1b3f3207a6c06dbe4f2bddeeb245da6716b70f54e9b1", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "The Disclosing Party assumes no responsibility for any loss or damages suffered by the Receiving Party or any third party caused by or arising from the Confidential Information, and the Disclosing Party makes no warranties of any kind, whether express or implied, as to the accuracy or completeness of the Confidential Information.\n\n1.6 Authorised.\n\n The Disclosing Party is authorised to provide Confidential Information to the Receiving Party.\n\n2. NON-DISCLOSURE\n\n2.1 Use of Confidential Information.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3900, "end_char_idx": 4402, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "d441c1fb-b051-4318-8f77-ee2d5d5584d8": {"__data__": {"id_": "d441c1fb-b051-4318-8f77-ee2d5d5584d8", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "719f133b-889a-47be-9bf0-7d3f7f8410c1", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "92b7d2ea440ec941bb40fc2a3da8a123eb3043a7567dc8b5cdbde4ec92b6bb44", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "45d33ea7-0ed7-43a6-82e6-790328a76d73", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "4a44084fb8c3bccc553ac1c4ecf5110b84bd78587fdaef2b2f0f2e89a7354e12", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "1b177b91-1813-4157-b51c-c65dc860ee7d", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "ec189f74a918b4b407585c227d5ccb596abf640fe428a3292411047dd9808ddb", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "The Receiving Party may use the Confidential Information solely for the purposes of assessing the Target for purposes of the Proposed Transaction.  The Receiving Party recognises that this Agreement imposes an affirmative duty to hold such information in confidence and protect it from dissemination to and use by any unauthorised persons. In the absence of the Disclosing Party\u2019s prior written consent, the Receiving Party shall not produce nor disclose the Confidential Information, or any part thereof, to any third party.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 4405, "end_char_idx": 4930, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "1b177b91-1813-4157-b51c-c65dc860ee7d": {"__data__": {"id_": "1b177b91-1813-4157-b51c-c65dc860ee7d", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "719f133b-889a-47be-9bf0-7d3f7f8410c1", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "92b7d2ea440ec941bb40fc2a3da8a123eb3043a7567dc8b5cdbde4ec92b6bb44", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "d441c1fb-b051-4318-8f77-ee2d5d5584d8", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "d96afd03fa68d282ddbf1b3f3207a6c06dbe4f2bddeeb245da6716b70f54e9b1", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "a2e8a91e-3386-4db4-b92d-c4706f88ae40", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f9a15a0cd0a85257192c3920ad40506265710a7fa38b8f1f561b4e2b6ffc3fb7", "class_name": "Relat